rows.name:
Hya hya hya!
The power of science, mo!

rows.label: tlk4240008104_msg0002
rows.name:
I used to be in Acedia, but now my lab,
tools, and money are all gone, mo.

rows.label: tlk4240008104_msg0003
rows.name:
I have no choice but to continue my research here,
crushing, mixing, and burning ores and herbs, but...

rows.label: tlk4240008104_msg0004
rows.name:
I'm running out of money to buy materials
to burn... mo. I have no choice but to work... mo.

rows.label: tlk4240008104_msg0005
rows.name:
Kyukyu hates manual labor, mo.
I don't want to work, mo...
